### Register user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student1",
  "email": "student1@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Login user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Create post (replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first forum post",
  "content": "This is my post content"
}

### List posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts

### Update post (replace POST_ID + TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "content": "Updated content"
}

### Toggle like on post (replace POST_ID + TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID/like
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Add comment (replace POST_ID + TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID/comments
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Great post"
}

### List comments (replace POST_ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID/comments

### Update comment (replace POST_ID + COMMENT_ID + TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID/comments/COMMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated comment"
}

### Delete comment (replace POST_ID + COMMENT_ID + TOKEN)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/posts/POST_ID/comments/COMMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Admin stats (requires admin/super token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

### Update user role (requires admin/super token)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/role
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "super"
}
